---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
const title = 'Web Search';
---

<DocsLayout title={title}>
<h1>Web Search</h1>
<p>Use the <code>web_search</code> tool to give the model access to current web information. You can also use <code>progrok search</code> directly from the CLI (no proxy needed).</p>
<h2>API Usage</h2>
<pre><code>{`curl -X POST http://localhost:18645/v1/chat/completions \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Latest news on AI"}],
    "tools": [{"type": "web_search"}]
  }'`}</code></pre>
<h2>CLI Usage</h2>
<pre><code>{`progrok search "latest AI news"`}</code></pre>
</DocsLayout>
